def table_game(table):
    a, b, c, d = table[0][0], table[0][2], table[2][0], table[2][2]
    guess = [[a, a + b, b], [a + c, a + b + c + d, b + d], [c, c + d, d]]
    return [a, b, c, d] if table == guess else [-1]

def table_game(table):
    top_left, top_right, bot_left, bot_right = table[0][0], table[0][-1], table[-1][0], table[-1][-1]
    top, bot, left, right = table[0][1], table[-1][1], table[1][0], table[1][-1]
    center = table[1][1]
    if (top_left + top_right == top and
        bot_left + bot_right == bot and
        top_left + bot_left == left and
        top_right + bot_right == right and
        top + bot == center):
        return [top_left, top_right, bot_left, bot_right]
    else:
        return [-1]

def table_game(table):
    return [table[i][j] for i in (0, 2) for j in (0, 2)] if all(table[0][i] + table[2][i] == table[1][i] and table[i][0] + table[i][2] == table[i][1] for i in range(3)) else [-1]
